<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Sepideh Pakseresht — Test Engineer</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
    :root{
      --bg:#04060f;
      --blue:#4f8fff;
      --blue2:#2563eb;
      --cyan:#38d9f5;
      --purple:#a78bfa;
      --glass:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      --glass-border:rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
      --glass-hover:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      --text:#f0f4ff;
      --muted:rgba(240,244,255,0.48);
      --syne:'Syne',sans-serif;
      --mono:'DM Mono',monospace;
    }
    html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
    body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--syne);overflow-x:hidden;cursor:none}

    /* CURSOR */
    #cursor{position:fixed;width:10px;height:10px;background:var(--blue);border-radius:50%;pointer-events:none;z-index:9999;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);transition:transform .2s,background .2s;mix-blend-mode:screen}
    #cursor-ring{position:fixed;width:36px;height:36px;border:1px solid rgba(79,143,255,0.4);border-radius:50%;pointer-events:none;z-index:9998;transform:translate(-50%,-50%)}

    /* BG */
    #bg-canvas{position:fixed;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;z-index:0;pointer-events:none}
    .orbs{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:0;pointer-events:none;overflow:hidden}
    .orb{position:absolute;border-radius:50%;filter:blur(110px);opacity:0.15;animation:drift 20s ease-in-out infinite}
    .orb1{width:650px;height:650px;background:radial-gradient(circle,#2563eb,transparent);top:-15%;left:-20%;animation-delay:0s}
    .orb2{width:500px;height:500px;background:radial-gradient(circle,#7c3aed,transparent);bottom:-10%;right:-15%;animation-delay:-8s}
    .orb3{width:380px;height:380px;background:radial-gradient(circle,#0891b2,transparent);top:38%;left:52%;animation-delay:-15s}
    @keyframes drift{0%,100%{transform:translate(0,0) scale(1)}33%{transform:translate(35px,-28px) scale(1.04)}66%{transform:translate(-18px,38px) scale(0.97)}}

    /* NAV */
    nav{position:fixed;top:24px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);z-index:100;display:flex;align-items:center;background:rgba(8,10,24,0.65);border:1px solid var(--glass-border);border-radius:100px;padding:0.45rem 0.45rem 0.45rem 1.5rem;backdrop-filter:blur(24px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(24px)}
    .nav-logo{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--blue);margin-right:2rem;letter-spacing:0.04em}
    .nav-links{display:flex;gap:0.2rem;list-style:none}
    .nav-links a{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;padding:0.42rem 1rem;border-radius:100px;letter-spacing:0.06em;transition:all .2s;font-family:var(--mono)}
    .nav-links a:hover,.nav-links a.active{color:var(--text);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07)}
    .nav-cta{margin-left:1rem;background:var(--blue2);color:#fff;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.06em;padding:0.48rem 1.2rem;border-radius:100px;text-decoration:none;transition:background .2s,transform .2s;white-space:nowrap}
    .nav-cta:hover{background:var(--blue);transform:scale(1.04)}

    /* HERO */
    .hero{min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;padding:7rem 6rem 5rem;position:relative;z-index:1}
    .hero-content{max-width:860px}
    .badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.6rem;background:rgba(79,143,255,0.09);border:1px solid rgba(79,143,255,0.22);border-radius:100px;padding:0.32rem 1rem;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--blue);letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:2.5rem}
    .badge-dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--cyan);animation:pulse 2.2s ease-in-out infinite}
    @keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1;box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(56,217,245,0.5)}55%{opacity:0.6;box-shadow:0 0 0 7px rgba(56,217,245,0)}}
    h1.hero-name{font-size:clamp(3.8rem,8.5vw,8.5rem);font-weight:800;line-height:0.93;letter-spacing:-0.04em;margin-bottom:1.6rem}
    .line1{display:block;color:var(--text)}
    .line2{display:block;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--blue) 0%,var(--cyan) 50%,var(--purple) 100%);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text}
    .typing-wrap{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:2.5rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem}
    .typing-prefix{color:rgba(79,143,255,0.55)}
    .cursor{display:inline-block;width:2px;height:0.9em;background:var(--cyan);animation:blink 1s step-end infinite;vertical-align:middle}
    @keyframes blink{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:0}}
    .hero-desc{font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--muted);max-width:520px;line-height:1.9;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:3.5rem}
    .hero-desc em{color:var(--text);font-style:normal;font-weight:500}
    .hero-ctas{display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap}
    .btn-glass{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.6rem;padding:0.85rem 2rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(37,99,235,0.8),rgba(79,143,255,0.55));border:1px solid rgba(79,143,255,0.38);border-radius:100px;color:#fff;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.07em;text-decoration:none;backdrop-filter:blur(10px);transition:all .25s;box-shadow:0 0 28px rgba(37,99,235,0.22)}
    .btn-glass:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 0 50px rgba(37,99,235,0.42)}
    .btn-outline{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.6rem;padding:0.85rem 2rem;background:var(--glass);border:1px solid var(--glass-border);border-radius:100px;color:var(--muted);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.07em;text-decoration:none;backdrop-filter:blur(10px);transition:all .25s}
    .btn-outline:hover{border-color:rgba(79,143,255,0.38);color:var(--text);transform:translateY(-3px)}

    /* GLASS */
    .glass{background:var(--glass);border:1px solid var(--glass-border);border-radius:20px;backdrop-filter:blur(20px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(20px);transition:border-color .25s,background .25s,transform .25s}
    .glass:hover{background:var(--glass-hover);border-color:rgba(79,143,255,0.22);transform:translateY(-4px)}

    /* SECTIONS */
    section{padding:7rem 6rem;position:relative;z-index:1}
    .section-inner{max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto}
    .sec-label{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--blue);letter-spacing:0.25em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:0.75rem}
    h2{font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3.2rem);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.03em;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:3.5rem;line-height:1.05}
    h2 span{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--blue),var(--cyan));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text}

    /* ABOUT */
    .about-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:3fr 2fr;gap:2rem;align-items:start}
    .about-card{padding:2.5rem}
    .about-card p{color:var(--muted);font-size:1rem;line-height:1.95;margin-bottom:1.3rem;font-weight:400}
    .about-card p:last-child{margin-bottom:0}
    .about-card p em{color:var(--text);font-style:normal;font-weight:500}
    .stats-col{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem}
    .stat-card{padding:1.75rem 2rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1.5rem}
    .stat-num{font-size:2.6rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.04em;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--blue),var(--cyan));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;line-height:1;flex-shrink:0}
    .stat-label{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);font-family:var(--mono);line-height:1.5}

    /* SKILLS */
    .skills-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.25rem}
    .skill-card{padding:1.75rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
    .skill-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--blue),var(--cyan),transparent);opacity:0;transition:opacity .25s}
    .skill-card:hover::before{opacity:1}
    .skill-num{font-size:2.8rem;font-weight:800;color:rgba(79,143,255,0.06);font-family:var(--mono);position:absolute;top:1rem;right:1.25rem;line-height:1}
    .skill-icon-wrap{width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:10px;background:rgba(79,143,255,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(79,143,255,0.18);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:1rem}
    .skill-cat{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--blue);letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:0.4rem}
    .skill-card h3{font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:1rem}
    .tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.4rem}
    .tag{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;padding:0.25rem 0.65rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:100px;color:var(--muted)}

    /* EXPERIENCE */
    .exp-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.25rem}
    .exp-card{padding:2.25rem 2.5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
    .exp-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:2px;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,var(--blue),transparent);opacity:0;transition:opacity .3s}
    .exp-card:hover::before{opacity:1}
    .exp-top{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:0.3rem}
    .exp-role{font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text)}
    .exp-badge{display:inline-block;background:rgba(56,217,245,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(56,217,245,0.22);border-radius:100px;padding:0.12rem 0.6rem;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--cyan);margin-left:0.5rem;vertical-align:middle;letter-spacing:0.06em}
    .exp-date{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0;padding-top:2px}
    .exp-co{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--blue);margin-bottom:1.1rem;letter-spacing:0.03em}
    .exp-desc{font-size:0.92rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.85;font-weight:400}

    /* EDUCATION */
    .edu-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.25rem}
    .edu-card{padding:1.75rem}
    .edu-icon{font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:0.85rem}
    .edu-title{font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:0.4rem}
    .edu-sub{font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--muted);font-family:var(--mono);line-height:1.65}

    /* CONTACT */
    .contact-card{padding:4rem;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:2rem}
    .contact-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 55% 55% at 50% 50%,rgba(37,99,235,0.1),transparent);pointer-events:none}
    .contact-card > p{color:var(--muted);font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.9;max-width:460px;margin:0 auto 2.75rem;font-weight:400}
    .contact-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1rem}
    .c-link{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;text-decoration:none;color:var(--text);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
    .c-link::after{content:'→';position:absolute;right:1.25rem;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%) translateX(5px);color:var(--blue);opacity:0;transition:opacity .2s,transform .2s}
    .c-link:hover::after{opacity:1;transform:translateY(-50%) translateX(0)}
    .c-icon{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:10px;flex-shrink:0;background:rgba(79,143,255,0.09);border:1px solid rgba(79,143,255,0.18);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--blue)}
    .c-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:2px}
    .c-sub{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--muted)}

    /* FOOTER */
    footer{padding:2rem 6rem;border-top:1px solid var(--glass-border);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);position:relative;z-index:1}

    /* SCROLL BAR */
    .scroll-line{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--blue),var(--cyan));z-index:200;width:0%;transition:width .08s linear}

    /* REVEAL */
    .reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px);transition:opacity .55s ease,transform .55s ease}
    .reveal.visible{opacity:1;transform:none}

    /* RESPONSIVE */
    @media(max-width:900px){
      nav{top:12px;padding:.4rem .4rem .4rem 1.2rem}
      .nav-links{display:none}
      .hero,section{padding:6rem 2rem 4rem}
      .about-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .skills-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
      .edu-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
      .contact-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .contact-card{padding:2.5rem 1.5rem}
      footer{padding:1.5rem 2rem;flex-direction:column;gap:.5rem;text-align:center}
    }
    @media(max-width:520px){
      h1.hero-name{font-size:3.5rem}
      .skills-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .edu-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div id="cursor"></div>
  <div id="cursor-ring"></div>
  <div class="scroll-line" id="scroll-line"></div>

  <div class="orbs">
    <div class="orb orb1"></div>
    <div class="orb orb2"></div>
    <div class="orb orb3"></div>
  </div>
  <canvas id="bg-canvas"></canvas>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav>
    <div class="nav-logo">sp.qa</div>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
      <li><a href="#experience">Experience</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
    <a href="mailto:sepiidehpakseresht@gmail.com" class="nav-cta">Say hello</a>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="badge"><span class="badge-dot"></span>Open to new opportunities</div>
      <h1 class="hero-name">
        <span class="line1">Sepideh</span>
        <span class="line2">Pakseresht</span>
      </h1>
      <div class="typing-wrap">
        <span class="typing-prefix">role://</span>
        <span id="typed"></span>
        <span class="cursor"></span>
      </div>
      <p class="hero-desc">
        I'm a Test Engineer who genuinely loves the process of building quality from the ground up.
        I work best when I'm close to the team — understanding the <em>why</em> behind every feature,
        not just the what.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="mailto:sepiidehpakseresht@gmail.com" class="btn-glass">Say hello ↗</a>
        <a href="#experience" class="btn-outline">See my work</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section id="about">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="sec-label">01 — About</div>
      <h2>A little about <span>me</span></h2>
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="glass about-card reveal">
          <p>
            I came to QA through a winding path — law school, product management, customer support,
            frontend development — and honestly, I think that's my biggest strength. I understand
            software from a lot of different angles, which makes me better at asking the questions
            that matter.
          </p>
          <p>
            What I love most is <em>building a test process from zero</em>. There's something
            deeply satisfying about looking at a new feature with no test coverage and turning it
            into something the whole team can ship with confidence.
          </p>
          <p>
            I'm most effective when I'm embedded in the team — in standups, in refinement sessions,
            in Slack threads with devs and designers. I don't just test at the end; I try to catch
            things before they're even built.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="stats-col">
          <div class="glass stat-card reveal">
            <div class="stat-num">4+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">years of professional<br>experience across tech</div>
          </div>
          <div class="glass stat-card reveal">
            <div class="stat-num">2</div>
            <div class="stat-label">QA roles at product<br>companies</div>
          </div>
          <div class="glass stat-card reveal">
            <div class="stat-num">C1</div>
            <div class="stat-label">English — CEFR<br>Advanced</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SKILLS -->
  <section id="skills">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="sec-label">02 — What I work with</div>
      <h2>Skills &amp; <span>tools</span></h2>
      <div class="skills-grid">
        <div class="glass skill-card reveal">
          <div class="skill-num">01</div>
          <div class="skill-icon-wrap">🧪</div>
          <div class="skill-cat">Core Testing</div>
          <h3>Manual & Functional</h3>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">Functional</span>
            <span class="tag">Regression</span>
            <span class="tag">Smoke</span>
            <span class="tag">Exploratory</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="glass skill-card reveal">
          <div class="skill-num">02</div>
          <div class="skill-icon-wrap">🔌</div>
          <div class="skill-cat">API Testing</div>
          <h3>APIs & Integrations</h3>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">Postman</span>
            <span class="tag">REST APIs</span>
            <span class="tag">Status codes</span>
            <span class="tag">Edge cases</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="glass skill-card reveal">
          <div class="skill-num">03</div>
          <div class="skill-icon-wrap">⚙️</div>
          <div class="skill-cat">Automation</div>
          <h3>Automation & CI/CD</h3>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">Cypress</span>
            <span class="tag">JMeter</span>
            <span class="tag">CI/CD pipelines</span>
            <span class="tag">Git</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="glass skill-card reveal">
          <div class="skill-num">04</div>
          <div class="skill-icon-wrap">📋</div>
          <div class="skill-cat">Planning</div>
          <h3>Test Planning & Tracking</h3>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">Jira</span>
            <span class="tag">Azure DevOps</span>
            <span class="tag">Test plans</span>
            <span class="tag">Bug reports</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="glass skill-card reveal">
          <div class="skill-num">05</div>
          <div class="skill-icon-wrap">🗄️</div>
          <div class="skill-cat">Dev & Data</div>
          <h3>Data & Dev Tools</h3>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">SQL</span>
            <span class="tag">JavaScript</span>
            <span class="tag">Chrome DevTools</span>
            <span class="tag">Figma</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="glass skill-card reveal">
          <div class="skill-num">06</div>
          <div class="skill-icon-wrap">🤝</div>
          <div class="skill-cat">Ways of Working</div>
          <h3>Agile & Collaboration</h3>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">Scrum</span>
            <span class="tag">Sprint planning</span>
            <span class="tag">Refinement</span>
            <span class="tag">Retrospectives</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EXPERIENCE -->
  <section id="experience">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="sec-label">03 — Where I've been</div>
      <h2>Work <span>experience</span></h2>
      <div class="exp-list">

        <div class="glass exp-card reveal">
          <div class="exp-top">
            <div>
              <div class="exp-role">QA Engineer <span class="exp-badge">Now</span></div>
              <div class="exp-co">TapsiShop</div>
            </div>
            <div class="exp-date">Jan 2026 — Present</div>
          </div>
          <p class="exp-desc">
            My current role — and the one where I've grown the most. I own test coverage for new
            features end-to-end, from writing test plans against backlog items all the way through
            exploratory and regression testing before release. A big part of my day is API testing
            in Postman and digging into SQL logs when something looks off. I work closely with
            backend, frontend, and design teams daily, and I genuinely enjoy being in the room
            where requirements get shaped — it's the best place to catch problems early.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass exp-card reveal">
          <div class="exp-top">
            <div>
              <div class="exp-role">QA & Product Quality Specialist</div>
              <div class="exp-co">Arico — B2B Marketplace</div>
            </div>
            <div class="exp-date">Sep 2025 — Jan 2026</div>
          </div>
          <p class="exp-desc">
            My first dedicated QA role, on a B2B marketplace platform. I got to design test cases
            for new features from scratch — which is exactly the kind of work I love. I handled
            functional, regression, and end-to-end testing, and got comfortable with REST API
            testing and Jira-based defect tracking. Short stint, but a big step.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass exp-card reveal">
          <div class="exp-top">
            <div>
              <div class="exp-role">Freelance Front-End Developer</div>
              <div class="exp-co">Independent</div>
            </div>
            <div class="exp-date">Jan 2024 — Present</div>
          </div>
          <p class="exp-desc">
            I build responsive web apps on the side — HTML, CSS, JavaScript. Doing this in parallel
            with QA work has been surprisingly valuable. When you've written the frontend yourself,
            you test it differently. You know where the edge cases hide.
          </p>
        </div>

